              throws java.lang.Exception
        Stores the data that is extracted by jSymboic for API use.
        Parameters:
        meiSpecificStorage - The mei specific data.
        aceXMLFeatureValue - The file for the ACE XML feature values.
        aceXMLFeatureDefinition - The file for the ACE XML feature definitions.
        arffFile - The file for the ARFF conversion. This can be null if no ARFF file is desired.
        csvArffFile - The file for the CSV conversion. This can be null if no CSV file is desired.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Thrown if the ACE XML could not be parsed into an ACE Databoard.
